      "span_text": "The goals of this study, done in conjunction with but separate from previously reported work  ), were to quantify morphological variation in four BLB color morphs, decipher genetic relationships among four different color phenotypes of BLB using genetic markers generated by amplified fragment length polymorphisms (AFLP), and investigate whether phenotypic differences between body color of the four BLB color morphs are reflected in genetic structure.",
